<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id063e4c0f-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDate" id="id063e4c10-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">For effective date of this section, see <ref href="/us/pl/108/19/s15">section 15 of Pub. L. 108–19</ref>, set out as a note under <ref href="/us/usc/t19/s3901">section 3901 of this title</ref>.</p>
